          Savio Education is a private education group developing a network of schools in France and internationally. Founded in 2021, its ambition is to promote an internationally inspired education within France, combining academic rigour, cultural openness, and holistic development.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Enguerrand Rochefort -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-32 h-32 lg:w-40 lg:h-40">
            <img
              src="/images/team/enguerrand-rochefort.avif"
              alt="Enguerrand Rochefort"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full border-4 border-[#c9a962]/20 group-hover:border-[#c9a962]/50 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl"
            />
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1e3d29] text-lg">Enguerrand Rochefort</h3>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] text-sm mt-2">President Savio International</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Benoît Bonnet -->
        <div class="group text-center">
          <div class="relative mb-4 mx-auto w-32 h-32 lg:w-40 lg:h-40">
